From: Performance Patch Series
Subject: [PATCH 08/16] 08-parallel-getobjects

Replace Parallel.ForEach with async Task.WhenAll chain.
Full async chain: GetCatalogsAsync -> GetDbSchemasAsync -> GetTableSchemasAsync
  -> GetColumnSchemaAsync / GetConstraintSchemaAsync
  -> GetConstraintColumnNamesAsync / GetConstraintsUsageAsync
Only one sync-over-async at the top-level GetCatalogs entry point.
Fixes Bug #4 (thread pool starvation) and Bug #5 (AggregateException wrapping).

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>

